excerpt from heudiconv help
If subject ID(s) is specified, it proceeds by extracting dicominfo from each subject and writing a config file $subject_id/$subject_id.auto.txt in the output directory. Users can create a copy of the file called $subject_id.edit.txt and modify it to change the files that are converted. This edited file will always overwrite the original file.
